import React, { Fragment } from 'react'
import { Col, Container, Row } from 'reactstrap'

const ChatBox = () => {
    return (

        // -------------------Main Section Chat Bar-------------//
        <Fragment>
            <Container>
                <Row>
                    <Col md={2}>
                        
                    </Col>
                    <Col md={4}>2</Col>
                    <Col md={6}>3</Col>
                </Row>
            </Container>
        </Fragment>
    )
}

export default ChatBox
